#: ../../source/yaml_config/index.rst:2
msgid "YAML Configuration Syntax"
msgstr "YAML 配置语法"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"Every IR-SIM scenario is a single YAML file with up to four top-level blocks:"
msgstr "每个 IR-SIM 场景都是一个 YAML 文件，最多包含四个顶层块："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/index.rst:6
msgid ""
"``world``: the simulation space, clock, coordinate frame, and obstacle map."
msgstr "``world`` —— 仿真空间、时钟、坐标系与障碍物地图。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"``robot``: one or more controllable robots (kinematics, shape, goal, "
"behavior, sensors)."
msgstr ""
"``robot`` —— 一个或多个可控机器人（运动学、形状、目标、行为、传感器）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/index.rst:8
msgid ""
"``obstacle``: static or dynamic obstacles. Robots and obstacles share the "
"**same object schema**, so any key valid for one is valid for the other."
msgstr ""
"``obstacle`` —— 静态或动态障碍物。机器人与障碍物共享**同一套对象模式**，因此"
"对其一有效的键对另一者同样有效。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/index.rst:9
msgid "``gui``: optional rendering and interaction options."
msgstr "``gui`` —— 可选的渲染与交互选项。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/index.rst:11
msgid ""
"The full reference below documents every key, with its default, and includes "
"an interactive schema explorer."
msgstr "下方的完整参考记录了每一个键及其默认值，并提供交互式的模式浏览器。"
